      "writtenOn": "2020-01-23T21:49:35Z",
      "side": 1,
      "message": "Another reason I forgot to mention is that I want to have some modules enabled by default in server.go (to split code into more manageable chunks). It means their implementation won\u0027t be able to import \u0027server\u0027 package due to a dependency cycle.",
      "parentUuid": "eb92d78f_aa4c25e0",
